Package uk.co.caprica.vlcj.player.events

A mechanism to encapsulate native media player events and dispatch notifications to event listeners.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    MediaPlayerEvent
    Specification for a media player event.
    VideoOutputEventListener Deprecated
    use MediaPlayerEventListener.videoOutput(MediaPlayer, int) instead, this class will be removed in vlcj 1.3.0
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MediaPlayerEventFactory
    A factory that creates a media player event instance for a native media player event or a semantic event.
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    MediaPlayerEventType
    Enumeration of media player event bit-masks.
